---
title: Sloppy Joe-Inspired Stew with Cheese Toast Soldiers
description: This riff on an American classic in stew form is served with some cheesy toast soldiers for soaking up all those retro flavours. The secret ingredient here is breadcrumbs, which thicken the stew to create the perfect consistency!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sloppy-joe-inspired-stew-a83e9fb4.jpg
